INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other modules which can be obtained from
the CPAN <http://cpan.org> if they are not allready installed on
your system :

  Carp
  File::Spec

